            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">5. Per-litter and per-animal financial attribution</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              How much did that kidding actually cost? What did you spend on that specific doe last year? What was net revenue per kid placed? BreederHQ rolls up expenses and revenue per litter, per animal, per breeding plan, and per calendar quarter, with Schedule C-mapped categories and quarterly tax export. One EasyKeeper reviewer on Capterra explicitly asked for more depth here: Sherry C. wrote, "I would like to track more financial aspects of feed and supplies."
