              The current system protocols ship for dogs and are being extended to species-appropriate templates across the other supported species. EasyKeeper does not publicly advertise a rearing protocol library for goats. Neither does any other multi-species or goat-specific competitor. Alongside Scout AI and native mobile, this is the third capability in this product category with no equivalent in the market today.
